name: insult (*user)
description: Generates an insult and targets someone.

name: dmthreaten (user; *custom_threat)
description: Sends a threat to a direct message channel of a user.

name: darkjoke
description: Sends a dark joke. May be insensitive.

name: dumbdeath (user)
description: Makes up a fictional scenario where the person you mentioned died a dumb death.
